name: Arief Said
review: (Translated by Google) The meatballs are delicious and chewy, the sauce is still clear and light, even though it's mixed with offal in the pot. Maybe it will be different if it comes at night, the gravy can be thicker and thicker. You can choose meatballs plus offal or plain. There are no drops / balungan. The white noodles use vermicelli, while the yellow ones use egg noodles. There's tofu pong as an addition and free pickled cucumber if it's still available... The place is a roadside tent which if it's full, it can get crowded and even queue up, even though there are two additional tables outside the tent... (Original) Baksonya enak dan kenyal, kuahnya tetep bening dan ringan, meski dicampur jeroan di dandangnya. Mungkin akan berbeda jika datangnya malam, kuah bisa lebih kental dan eneg. Bisa pilih bakso plus jeroan atau polos. Tidak ada tetelan /balungan. Mienya yang putih pake soun, sedang yang kuning mie telor. Ada tahu pong sebagai tambahan dan free acar timun jika masih ada... Tempatnya tenda pinggir jalan yang jika penuh, bisa sesak bahkan ngantri, meski ada dua meja tambahan di luar tenda...

name: Regina FY
review: (Translated by Google) Try this Baso at night, the location is next to the transmart near the intersection. Ask the father, it is open from 12.30 to 21.00, the price of the Baso is IDR 19,000 per serving. How does it feel? Yummy The bass is bouncy, supple, solid, not soft when you bite it. The gravy is hot too. The sambal is spicy Then earlier, we were making dinner so we beat the rice too. The rice is delicious too, fluffier, clean white. There are ready to swallow/offal too, just because it was finished, it's not there anymore. You can choose vermicelli or yellow noodles too. On the table there is a choice of fried tofu as well as snacks to eat with the baso. Overall it's delicious, if you go to Semarang again, this will be on the list of Must-Try Foods (Original) Nyobain Baso ini pas kulineran malem, lokasi di samping transmart deket simpang lima itu. Nanya si bapak nya buka dari jam 12.30 sampai jam 21.00, Harga Baso nya IDR 19,000 per porsi. Rasa nya gimana ? Enakkk Baso nya mantul, kenyel, padet, gak gembos gt digigit. Kuah nya juga panas. Sambel nya pedessss Trus tadi kita-kita kan buat makan malem jadi hajar nasi juga. Nasi nya enak juga, pulen, putih bersih. Ada sedia tetelan/jeroan juga, cuma krn tadi penghabisan, uda gak ada. Bisa pilih bihun atau mie kuning juga. Di meja ada pilihan tahu goreng juga buat cemal cemil makan sama si baso. Overall enak, klo ke Semarang lagi, ini bakal masuk list Makanan Wajib Coba

name: Arum Ryan
review: (Translated by Google) For those who also like to eat meatballs, this is one of the meatballs that I recommend for you. My real favorite is the dumplings and 1 bowl is not enough. This location is in an alleyway and the place is not that big but it's always busy. 1 portion of meatballs gets 5 small fine meatballs and 1 meatball that is filled with veins and then there are pieces of tripe/offal . Inframes: Meatballs + free dumplings 13k . The beef meatballs are really good and very chewy, the meat tastes really good. The broth is light, the broth tastes great. The veined meatballs aren't the typical grenyel, but the stuffing just melts in your mouth! Don't forget to dip the gravy with the dumplings. It's really really crunchy, it's not just the dumplings, the dumplings also have stuffing, so it's more textured, these dumplings remind me of the dumplings at Bakso Patience waiting behind Gramedia. Krn delicious, tasty, not hard and crunchy. What a fav! (Original) Sebagai yg gemar juga makan bakso, ini salah 1 bakso yg rekomen juga buat kalian. Asli favorit bgt pangsitnya dan gak cukup 1 mangkok. Ini lokasinya masuk gang gt dan tempatnya ga begitu luas tpselalu rame. 1 porsi bakso dpt 5 bakso halus kecil dan 1 bakso sedang isi urat gitu trus ada potongan babat/jeroan . In frame: üç¥Bakso + free pangsit üí∏ 13k . üìå Baksonya bakso sapi yg bener2 alus trus kenyal bgt, berasa bgt dagingnya. Kuahnya light, berasa bgt kaldunya. Kalo bakso uratnya bukan tipikal yg grenyel tp isian uratnya langsung melt di mulut! Kuahnya sih jgn lupa dicocol pake pangsitnya. Bener2 kranciii bgt, ga cuma kranci doang, pangsitnya juga ada isiannya gt lo jd makin bertekstur, ini pangsit ngingetin aku sama pangsit di Bakso Sabar menanti belakang Gramedia. Krn enak, gurih, gak keras dan renyah. Emang fav bgt!

name: fahmi aqwa
review: (Translated by Google) Mie ayam and meatball "watu kelir" Some time ago I accidentally passed by Jalan Suyudono, the rain finally calmed down. Now from the shelter I saw a chicken noodle shop which was quite busy but because it was still full, I didn't stop by So, coincidentally, today I wanted to eat chicken noodles, so I finally got time to try it. Stopped by here. And thank God the taste of the chicken noodles matched, the noodles had the right texture, not too smooth and not too big, the chicken topping was quite a lot and the seasoning wasn't strong but still taste good, over all good, just don't like the meatball texture. For the price itself, it is still friendly and safe in the pocket, for the portion which I think is a lot. (Original) Mie ayam dan bakso "watu kelir" Beberapa waktu lalu nggak sengaja lewat jaln suyudono,terua hujan akhirnya neduh.nah dari tempat berteduh tampak kedai mie ayam yang lumayan rame tapi karena masih kenyang jadi nggak mampir Nah kebetulan hari ini lagi pengen makan mie ayam,akhirnya di sempwtin buat cobain.mampir ke sini.dan alhmadulillah taste mie ayamnya cocok,mienya teksturnya pas bentuknya juga nggak terlalu halus dan nggak terlalu besar,toping ayamnya lumayan banyak dan bumbunya bukan yang kuat tapi tetep berasa,over all enak ,cuman kurang suka tektur baksonya. Untuk harga sendiri masih bersahabat aman di kantong,untuk porsi yang menurut saya banyak.

review: (Translated by Google) Strategic place on the side of the road, but for car parking it can't fit in front of it. Next time please pay attention to who comes first the queue. Success needs to be maintained. Onclang/scallions and pickled cucumbers are not available, or are they out of stock, I don't know, it's best if each table is provided with pickled cucumbers and scallions in their own bowls/places, so that customers can take whatever they like. For the taste, it's okay... If you're hungry, it's delicious.... (Original) Tempat strategis pinggir jalan, tapi untuk parkir mobil tidak bisa pas di depannya. Onclang/daun bawang dan timun acarnya ga ada, ato emang kehabisan ga tau, sebaiknya tiap meja disediakan timun acar dan daun bawang di mangkok/tempat sendiri, sehingga pelanggan bisa mengambil sesuai selera.
